cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with scene parsing, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) as a parametric model, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of a global energy term and a non-parametric framework, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language), respectively. Finally, the paper mentions achieving state-of-the-art results on benchmarks, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
